<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Café Desserts Menu</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f1e5;
            color: #5c3d2e;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #5c3d2e;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .menu-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #8b5e3b;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #5c3d2e;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .menu-item {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .menu-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .menu-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #5c3d2e;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .menu-item p {
            margin: 5px 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        Café Desserts Menu
    </header>

    <div class="menu-container">
        <h2>Cakes & Pastries</h2>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Chocolate Cake <span>₹250</span></h3><p>Rich, moist cake with layers of chocolate frosting or ganache.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Cheesecake <span>₹300</span></h3><p>Creamy dessert made with cream cheese on a crumbly biscuit base.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Tiramisu <span>₹350</span></h3><p>Italian no-bake dessert with coffee-soaked ladyfingers and mascarpone.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Black Forest Cake <span>₹280</span></h3><p>Chocolate cake layered with cherries, whipped cream, and chocolate shavings.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Éclair <span>₹180</span></h3><p>French pastry filled with custard or cream, topped with chocolate glaze.</p></div>

        <h2>Cookies & Biscuits</h2>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Macarons <span>₹200</span></h3><p>Delicate French almond meringue cookies with a flavored filling.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Brownies <span>₹150</span></h3><p>Dense, fudgy or cakey chocolate bars, sometimes with nuts.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Shortbread Cookies <span>₹120</span></h3><p>Buttery, crumbly cookies with a melt-in-the-mouth texture.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Snickerdoodles <span>₹130</span></h3><p>Soft cinnamon-sugar-coated cookies with a slight tangy flavor.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Oatmeal Raisin Cookies <span>₹140</span></h3><p>Chewy cookies made with oats, raisins, and cinnamon.</p></div>

        <h2>Cold & Creamy Desserts</h2>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Ice Cream <span>₹180</span></h3><p>A frozen dairy treat in countless flavors like vanilla and chocolate.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Gelato <span>₹200</span></h3><p>Italian-style ice cream with a denser and creamier texture.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Sorbet <span>₹160</span></h3><p>A dairy-free frozen dessert made from fruit puree and sugar.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Panna Cotta <span>₹220</span></h3><p>Silky Italian dessert made from sweetened cream and gelatin.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Mousse <span>₹190</span></h3><p>Light and airy dessert made with whipped cream, chocolate, or fruit puree.</p></div>

        <h2>Puddings & Traditional Sweets</h2>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Rice Pudding <span>₹140</span></h3><p>Comforting dessert made from rice, milk, sugar, and spices.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Crème Brûlée <span>₹250</span></h3><p>French custard dessert with a caramelized sugar crust.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Bread Pudding <span>₹180</span></h3><p>Baked dessert made from bread soaked in a sweet, spiced custard.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Gulab Jamun <span>₹100</span></h3><p>Indian sweet made of deep-fried dough balls soaked in sugar syrup.</p></div>
        <div class="menu-item"><h3>Mochi <span>₹220</span></h3><p>Japanese rice cake with a chewy texture, often filled with sweet bean paste.</p></div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
